\noindent{\bf Datasets:}

We use two book datasets, Goodreads [wan2018item] (GR) and Amazon books [ni2019justifying] (AM), from the UCSD recommender systems repository [McAuleyDatasets].
Both datasets contain item titles, genre or category tags, item description, and user reviews.